## FAQ

- **Why isn’t shadcn-svelte next published as an npm package?**  
  The source code is provided so you have full control over the implementation and styling, allowing for maximum customization.

- **Which frameworks are supported?**  
  shadcn-svelte next is built for Svelte/SvelteKit and is designed to work seamlessly with Svelte 5.

